headline: Should You Forget Palantir and Buy These 2 Artificial Intelligence (AI) Stocks Instead?
summary: While it's well off its recent highs, Palantir Technologies (NASDAQ: PLTR) was one of the best-performing stocks in 2024 and early 2025.  The company has been seeing accelerating revenue growth, with revenue climbing 36% last quarter, led by a 64% jump in U.S. commercial revenue.  Palantir aims to become an AI operating system for its users, creating a platform that can help organizations run AI applications in a real-world environment.
